headline: Johnson & Johnson Presents Early Outcomes from the OMNY-AF Pilot Study at 2026 AF Symposium
summary: IRVINE, Calif., February 07, 2026--Johnson & Johnson announced 12-month pilot-phase data from the OMNY-AF study and highlighted new findings related to the VARIPULSE Platform.
